# 💡 Key Insights

### 1️⃣ Data roles are in high demand

Data Scientists, Data Engineers, and Data Analysts dominate job postings globally.

---

### 2️⃣ Specialized roles earn higher salaries

Machine Learning Engineers and Data Engineers earn significantly more due to advanced technical skills.

---

### 3️⃣ Geography heavily impacts salary

The United States and developed markets offer much higher compensation compared to other regions.

---

### 4️⃣ Full-time employment dominates

The majority of job postings are full-time roles rather than contract positions.

---

### 5️⃣ LinkedIn is the top hiring platform

Most companies rely on LinkedIn to recruit data professionals.

